  <brief_title>Mesenchymal Stem Cells Infusion for aGVHD Prophylaxis Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study for Safety and Effectiveness Assessment of Bone Marrow Mesenchymal Stem Cell Infusion for Acute Graft-versus-host Disease Prophylaxis and Treatment After Allogenic Bone Marrow Transplantation</official_title>
