  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Infusion of Mesenchymal Stem Cell (MSC) at day of recovery after bone marrow transplant (BMT)
      for patients with AL, AA and MM for acute Graft-versus-host Disease (GVHD) prophylaxis and
      treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Infusion of mesenchymal stem cells at day of recovery after BMT for patients with AL, AA and
      MM for acute GVHD prophylaxis and treatment. Infusion at dose 1 cells mln/kg at day of white
      blood cells recovery.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
